DynamicEntity Class

In this Article

Provides an ASP.NET control that represents an entity for use by ASP.NET Dynamic Data.

Remarks

This control can be used to load a control from the DynamicData\EntityTemplates folder. The control must derive from EntityTemplateUserControl.

For a tutorial series on using model binding with Web Forms, which includes the use a DynamicEntity control, see Model Binding and Web Forms.

Declarative Syntax

<asp:DynamicEntity  
    ID="string"  
    Mode="string"  
    ValidationGroup="string"  
    OnLoad="On load event handler"/>
